{"tid":108160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美食車是戇居到無倫的計劃","createTime":"2017-02-05T04:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T04:08:31.000Z","uid":2503,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"965521ac2a7948d969983fc9c408c0f96c48ff90","tid":108160,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"「美食車」的美學與修辭問題。曾俊華倡議的food truck，本來已經是戇居到無倫的計劃，將低成本、高手藝的平民熟食木頭車仔士紳化，好似九十年代的仆街集團茶樓將魚蛋豬皮放入羊城點心的範圍。改了個中文名「美食車」，更加是離地黐線幼稚白痴小資中產的名字，陀衰香港。<br />\n<br />\n以前殖民地時代，街市大廈賣粥麵、茶水的地方，老老實實就叫熟食市場，不會叫美食市場的。正如寫文章的人，不會說自己在寫美文（belles lettres）。只是膚淺、小器、矯情、沒見過世面的人，才會叫自己的熟食車做美食車，而曾俊華就是這種格局的人。曾俊華這種人，非常之符合泛民及泛民的支持者追捧，因為一樣的膚淺、小器、矯情、沒見過世面。"},{"pid":"cb745ee9ed398c1d0355b124c1b4725603907a08","tid":108160,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"黃絲飯民：你鬧曾俊華，係唔係想幫林鄭抬轎呀，唔通你認為林鄭做特首又會好咩"},{"pid":"8af34f3df1e0c23bd89af43d0bfb3952879870ba","tid":108160,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:53:15.000Z","msg":"論點幾新鮮，起碼我係第二度未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一言驚醒洛克人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個名真係好嬌情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看透世事連登仔：一早知美食車戇居啦仲洗你講！"},{"pid":"1339f0498400ed38cc38dab13239dc2f47a92ca2","tid":108160,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"如果可以再多啲美食車就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4c97505fd0e64409df5fad203eb022250aa92e","tid":108160,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"政府單純係諗寓禁於徵<br />\n你班柒頭就上綱上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eba554feca6ffa65151fd952d0020d5960675e","tid":108160,"uid":875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"咁請問food truck譯美食車有咩問題？唔通難聽到叫做食物車？"},{"pid":"f05b092b8c4dbc77551e1f1088aafdcf39ac9a91","tid":108160,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"冇嘢好屌就屌個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3605f30cc61a1c4d00661f72fa279bb12ee752d9","tid":108160,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"西環打手出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b25a8dd70c436153596bc75ac0e5f424c446182","tid":108160,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"美食車數目太少就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d2f18144282d26763d29f7fd880f96183d5626","tid":108160,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"事實上佢依種係外國引入既叫美食車真係無乜問題，只不過賣既野港式化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n木頭車個規模邊有美食車咁大"},{"pid":"2e881a6243cab20b01597d801220ce0237aeb03f","tid":108160,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"native"},{"pid":"0d74d249fab261fe6938c8a41a13f7883ad70ba1","tid":108160,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"無野好屌屌個名？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑死</span></span>"},{"pid":"0574bbace28ade80eae70a79c6871f40d654fef6","tid":108160,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"架車仲貴過幾年租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9d9c0d11a391fab74b7d35ed288266fc1ddc7e","tid":108160,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime